## Getting Started

This project is a working minimal application that you can start immediately.

### Development Server

To start a local development server, run:

```bash
npm run dev
```

The application will be available on localhost with the port shown in your terminal output.

You can test if everything is working by opening your browser and navigating to the displayed URL.
