## Adding New Services and Entities

You can add new services and entities manually by following the existing project structure, or use the Onion-Initializr CLI for automated generation.

### Using the CLI Tool

Install the CLI globally:

```bash
npm install -g onion-initializr
```

Then use it to generate new files:

```bash
onion
```

For more information, visit the [CLI documentation](https://www.npmjs.com/package/onion-initializr).

